# JSDoc Standards

## Every Exported Component
```tsx
/**
 * Hero section — first visible section of the portfolio.
 * Displays name, headline, subparagraph, CTAs and photo.
 *
 * @remarks
 * Client component — uses framer-motion animations and
 * scroll utilities.
 */
export function Hero() { ... }
```

